{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be user-friendly and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureNet Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #e53935; /* Red brand color */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #c62828 3px solid;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/e53935/ffffff?text=SecureNet+Cybersecurity') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 500px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #e53935;\n        }\n        .service-item, .about-item {\n        